Jeff Manning https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff_Manning 0 Jeff Manning, sometimes credited as Jeffrey Manning, is an English language voice actor who is known primarily for his work on the North American English dub of Iron Chef, as well as roles in several video games and voice-overs on numerous television commercials. He previously worked for Mickey's Company, an agency based in Japan (as credited in the original Super Smash Bros.). He now works for Triple Sun Talent, another agency based in Japan.
